Prerequisites:
--------------

1. Install brew

2. Install brew packages:

  for i in gmp mpfr libmpc libiconv deja-gnu libusb-compat libelf
  do
    brew install $i
  done

3. Install Xcode

Build:
------

1. sh build.sh

Pack:
-----

1. PackageMaker package/*.pmdoc, review as necessary. Go to
PackageRoot -> Configuration -> Install, add a dummy letter
then delete it to force tree reload. Bump version if
necessary.

2. Click build package

